# e.g., "🔥 Add missing parameters", "🔖 0.5.2"

# ================================================
# = Commit Message Format
# ================================================
# <PREFIX> <SUMMARY>
# 
# <DESCRIPTION>
# ================================================
#
# ===========================================
# = PREFIX
# ===========================================
# + One of these
#   🎉: Initial commit
#   🔖: Version tag
#   ✨: New features
#   🔥: Bugfixes
#   🛡: Security improvements
#   🕹️: UI improvements
#   🚀: Performance improvements
#   🔋: Energy saving Improvements
#   💎: Formatting
#   💫: Refactoring
#   💣: Breaking changes
#   ➕: Adding dependencies
#   ➖: Removing dependencies
#   ⬆: Upgrading dependencies
#   ⬇: Downgrading dependencies
#   🧪: Tests
#   📚: Documentation
#   💚: Continuous Integration
#   📦: Packaging
#   🛠: Tools
#   ⚙️: Configuration
#   🚧: Work In Progress
#   🗑: Reverting changes
#   🔀: Merging
#   ⚡: Others
#
# ===========================================
# = SUMMARY
# ===========================================
# + 1-50 characters
# + Single line
#
# ===========================================
# = DESCRIPTION
# ===========================================
# + 0-72 characters
# + Single line or multiple lines
#
